Name: New Balance Cardiff City FC Training 1/4 Zip Top
Description: Gear up for the pitch like the pros in this men's Cardiff City FC Training 1/4 Zip Top from New Balance. Coming in a Navy and Sky Blue colourway, this training top is made with smooth, lightweight poly fabric for essential comfort. Crafted with sweat-wicking NB DRY tech, it features a quarter zip closure and a raised collar to adjust your airflow. It has long, raglan-cut sleeves for maximum movement, while thumb loops deliver a secure, streamlined fit. Finished up with New Balance branding to the chest, and the iconic Cardiff City FC crest to sign off. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 38" chest and wears a size medium.

Name: adidas Match Tracksuit
Description: Double up your training heat with this men's Match Tracksuit from adidas. Landing in a JD-exclusive Mystery Blue colourway, this pitch-ready set is made from durable recycled poly fabric, and uses sweat-wicking AEROREADY tech to keep you cool. The track top has a full zip fastening, mock collar and ribbed trims for essential coverage, while the pants feature an elasticated drawcord waistband, tapered legs and side pockets. Finished off with Volt 3-Stripes down the sides and a Badge of Sport logo to the chest and thigh. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'1" with a 36.5" chest and wears a size medium. | HY2892

Name: Puma Borussia Dortmund Pre-Match Sweatshirt
Description: Stay covered on the pitch and in the stands with this men's Borussia Dortmund Pre-Match Sweatshirt from PUMA. In a Black colourway, this collared jumper is made from super-smooth and durable poly fabric, with added stretch to the trims for support. It uses sweat-wicking dryCELL tech for cool comfort, and features thumb loops to hold the sleeves in place. Finished off with tonal Puma Cat branding and the iconic BVB logo to the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 35" chest and wears a size medium.

Name: Puma Anzarun
Description: Update your rotation with these men's Anzarun sneakers from PUMA. Exclusive to JD, these kicks have a lightweight woven upper with smooth synthetic skin details for added support. They feature a tonal lace fastening with plush padding around the ankle collar for a locked-in fit, and sit atop a spongy foam midsole for a cushioned step. With a tough rubber outsole for grippy traction, they're finished up with PUMA's iconic Formstrip to the sidewalls. Signed off with classic PUMA branding.

It features short sleeves with a v-neckline and is signed off with Raiders branding, a Swoosh to the sleeve and Carr #4 printed to the back. Machine washable | Our model is 5'11" with a 38" chest and wears a size medium.

With mesh inserts to the sides to keep you cool, this shirt is finished up with adidas branding and the legendary Belgium crest. Machine washable.|HD9413

Name: Nike Air Max 90
Description: Upgrade your sneaks with these men's Air Max 90 trainers from Nike. They feature a lace fastening to lock you in and a low-cut padded ankle collar for plush comfort. Underfoot is a foam midsole that uses Nike Air cushioning combined with a visible Air unit to the heel for an ultra-responsive ride. With a rubber Waffle outsole for total traction, they're finished up with the Swoosh to the sidewalls.
